    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "Units that aren't planes don't have a straight attack function. You have to use something like AttackMove. You can see this on the [Lua API](https://github.com/OpenRA/OpenRA/wiki/Lua-API). This means that the actor doesn't have that particular function for future reference:\n\n`Actor 'e1' does not define a property 'Attack'`\n"
