    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "This is just a bit of a workaround but you could do this:\n\n`allies.SetStance(\"neutral\", \"Enemy\")`\n`unit.AttackMove(waypoint94.Location)`\n`Trigger.OnKilled(barrel, function() allies.SetStance(\"neutral\",\"Ally\") end)`\n\nOf course you could also just make neutral an enemy from the start but that might make them hunt barrels instead of attack the player. I'd give it a try though or try you might this:\n\n`barrel.Owner = soviets`\n"
  },
